{
  "stem": "14060.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "British did not give an extending help, maybe under Arab pressure in the '30s, the mufti and all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also, may have been due to the extended families people had, leave behind grandparents or children or brothers and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't a simple just pick yourself up and go, and forget about your past, your family, and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In those days, to go from Hungary to Palestine was a very long way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You didn't have flights in two hours or three hours to get there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was basically meant to be maybe for a lifetime.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they could have been personal reasons, maybe there was somebody ill in the family or whatever, that families like to keep together, at least those days, they did.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody was looking to break up a family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unfortunately, in our part of the world, people were extremely correct, too correct I would say, to the point of having their honor placed in the hands of the Hungarian management of the country.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And once there were many-- as you told me yourself, your parents or grandparents came from Russia-- we did not have this mass immigrations coming due to pogroms.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only people practically-- and I've got to be excused if I make a mistake, because there were very nice people who left as well for different reasons or had the sense to escape in time.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people who did something incorrect, let's say they passed a check which wasn't met, they could not stay in that town anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People-- the Jews or the non-Jews were not prepared to deal with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what did they do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went up to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a big city and they could get lost.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
